  • Constructor Details

    • PBlockData

      public PBlockData(ICustomCraftFallingBlock newFBlock, float radius, INMSBlock newBlock, IPLocation startLocation, float startAngle, boolean placementDeferred)
      Constructs of PBlockData.
      Parameters:
      newFBlock - The ICustomCraftFallingBlock that will be animated.
      radius - The number of blocks between this block and the rotation point.
      newBlock - If this block can be rotated, this contains the rotated INMSBlock.
      startLocation - The location the block was spawned at initially.
      startAngle - The angle the block had in regards to the rotation point when it was first spawned.
      placementDeferred - Whether or not placement should be deferred until all standalone blocks are placed. Useful for torches, for example (so they don't fall off immediately).
